Dawn... precious young ladies like you have paid the price for world resistance to tyranny.  You paid a terrific price and still pay today... I would be honored to have you stand by my side when the Colors go by.<br>
Young people like you make my two trips to Viet Nam more meaningful for me.<br>
God Bless You, Sweetheart, God Bless Your Daddy... and God Bless America.<br><br>
Your Faithful Servant<br><br>
Edward Ramon, RVN '66-'67-'69
